name: AirTemperature
description: Temperature is a measure of the average kinetic energy of translation of the gas molecules.

name: RelativeHumidity
description: Humidity is the concentration of water vapor present in the air.

name: PM10
description: inhalable particles, with diameters that are generally 10 micrometers and smaller.

name: PM25
description: inhalable particles, with diameters that are generally 2.5 micrometers and smaller

name: NO2
description: Nitrogen dioxide is a chemical compound with the formula NO2

name: SoundPressure
description: Sound pressure or acoustic pressure is the local pressure deviation from the ambient (average or equilibrium) atmospheric pressure, caused by a sound wave
